  Vesper Book
DEUS, qui in corde beátæ Gertrúdis Vírginis jucúndam tibi mansiónem præparásti: ipsíus méritis et intercessióne; cordis nostri máculas cleménter abstérge, et ejúsdem tríbue gaudére consórtio. Per Dóminum.
O GOD, who, in the heart of blessed Gertrude, didst prepare for thyself an acceptable dwelling place, mercifully cleanse our hearts from all stain through her merits and intercession, and grant unto us to rejoice with her in glory. Through our Lord.
